Cape Town - Police destroyed about 23 000 firearms - a move Gun Free South Africa (GFSA) welcomed.GFSA director Adele Kirsten said, Destroying these guns takes them out of circulation and this helps make our communities safer. Sonke Gender Justice s Nonhlanhla Skosana said the destruction of illegal guns talks to the lives of women, because many women are shot and killed by their partners.Weekend Argus